      <div class="landmark">
        <p>We are working hard on creating a simple, transparent and accesible data &amp; privacy policy. You can read about our efforts on <a href="https://medium.com/@vai_kai/privacy-of-toys-ed61bac940cd#.gtg2pfos9" target="_blank">our blog</a>.</p>
        <p>In the meantime, as we are a German company, we are obliged to provide the following standard text describing the privacy policy of the website.</p>
